title: Spyeco.4K.Demo.Content.UHD.3840x2160
description:
Kaleidoscope Test Content - Video Wall

Art: Source_Image.jpg
Codec: Divx HEVC (H.265)
Container: .mkv
Duration: 30 seconds


Note: Divx Player is required for playback - http://www.divx.com/

Video files where created for test playback on videos walls up to 3x3 configuration up to 4K. Optimal playback requires desktop resolution set to match video resolution.  

Minimum Computer Specs for Video Wall 3x3 4K Playback

CPU: 3 Ghz Six Core Processor or better
Ram: Daul Channel (2 x 4GB sticks, 8GB total)
Operating System: Windows Seven Professional 64Bit
Graphics Card: Combine 2 AMD Firepro W600 Graphics Cards
Hard Drive: Solid State Drive 


Content tested using Spyeworks Digital Signage software. Single Computer driving 3x3 Video wall.
